    <briefdescription>
<para>This class allows to extract content (text, tables, attachments) from the .pdf documents with a textual layer with broken encoding (copyable documents, but copied text is incorrect) with complex background. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It uses a pdfminer library for text extraction and CNN for font&apos;s glyphs prediction. Currently, only Russian and English languages are supported.</para>
<para>For more information, look to <computeroutput>pdf_with_text_layer</computeroutput> option description in :ref:<computeroutput>pdf_handling_parameters</computeroutput>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
